ScrumMastor
-----------

This project serves as an api backend for the ScrumMastorClient project.

To install:
 - install pear if necessary: sudo apt-get install php5-dev php5-cli php-pear
 - install the mongo extension: sudo pecl install mongo
 - enable ext-mongo: add extension=mongo.so to /etc/php5/cli/php.ini
 - restart apache: sudo service apache2 restart
 - git clone git@github.com:eleven-labs/ScrumMastor.git
 - composer install
 - vi config/default.php and use your config
 
For Mongo, you can use http://www.mongohq.com
 
All is done, your project is ready.
